issue.title: build: Remove unused RES_IMAGES
issue.body:
Remove RES_IMAGES. Seems to be unused since 2015 in the commit below.

https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/commit/98c222b5aa94543fce683b989356b0d8ad1f1d22#diff-9a4f3a253de77bf90b107bdf5283ebc3R317

The src/qt/res/images to which it was used with is no longer present either.

events.body: @hebasto Will do. Not seen that repo before.

~0 on this, but if you really want to change this all over the repository in a shitton of files, I think this should be a scripted diff.
See https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/master/doc/developer-notes.md#scripted-diffs
@hebasto thanks. I'll close this PR and create one on gui using a scripted diff.
